{"id":101800,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/用iphone挑西瓜，行吗？/","date":"2010-08-30T17:48:19Z","modified":"2010-08-30T17:48:19Z","title":"用iPhone挑西瓜，行吗？","content":"<p><p>来自: <a href=\"http://www.feedzshare.com/b/2857/2\">Beta Show &#8211; FeedzShare</a>  <br />\n<br />发布时间:2010年08月29日,  已有 5 人推荐 </p>\n<hr>\n<div>\n<p><div><span>不知道移动2.0周刊的读者中，有多少是“挑西瓜”高手？</span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span>我反正这方面比较弱智，每次买西瓜都把决定权交给了卖家，让Ta帮我挑一个沙甜的，不过并不是都如愿以偿，虽然说我相信卖家并不是存心骗我，但是有时候卖家的挑西瓜能力是不是也值得怀疑？</span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span>偶尔发现了一款iPhone应用，彻底解决了这个问题，这款应用叫iWatermelon（<a title=\"点击这里进入iTunes下载\" href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/cn/app/iwatermelon-deluxe/id367961174?mt=8\">点击这里进入iTunes下载</a>）</span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span>第一步，一起打开软件，选择西瓜的尺寸，选择西瓜的颜色：</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div><img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4122/4760650362_50dca1671f_m.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://geo.yahoo.com/f?s=792600099&#038;t=e1d2713a2ddd85966d96fc95ea4048c2&#038;r=http://www.flickr.com/photos/betashow2006/4760650362/sizes/o/&#038;fl_ev=0&#038;lang=en&#038;intl=us\" alt=\"\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" /></td>\n<td>\n<div><img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4134/4760652604_faffc8c5da_m.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://geo.yahoo.com/f?s=792600099&#038;t=7c8f413b0f090f3b31220ff82117519f&#038;r=http://www.flickr.com/photos/betashow2006/4760652604/sizes/o/&#038;fl_ev=0&#038;lang=en&#038;intl=us\" alt=\"\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" /></td>\n<td>\n<div><img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4100/4760019917_bf09f7d75d_m.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://geo.yahoo.com/f?s=792600099&#038;t=35e76f35b8960cae834a75f256a585f9&#038;r=http://www.flickr.com/photos/betashow2006/4760019917/sizes/o/in/photostream/&#038;fl_ev=0&#038;lang=en&#038;intl=us\" alt=\"\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" /></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>接下来，我们把iPhone放到西瓜上，然后1，2，3，敲三次：</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div><img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4137/4760021027_f9b128465f_m.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://geo.yahoo.com/f?s=792600099&#038;t=0793dd17e62f85cd5c67dda757f567a4&#038;r=http://www.flickr.com/photos/betashow2006/4760021027/sizes/o/in/photostream/&#038;fl_ev=0&#038;lang=en&#038;intl=us\" alt=\"\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" /></td>\n<td>\n<div><img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4134/4760656928_000466c455_m.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://geo.yahoo.com/f?s=792600099&#038;t=3f79169704830dffb4f925406159a024&#038;r=http://www.flickr.com/photos/betashow2006/4760656928/sizes/o/in/photostream/&#038;fl_ev=0&#038;lang=en&#038;intl=us\" alt=\"\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" /></td>\n<td>\n<div><img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4136/4760658630_d3b0d60022_m.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://geo.yahoo.com/f?s=792600099&#038;t=4dc9772cd19cf24c6c3ec151c738bc16&#038;r=http://www.flickr.com/photos/betashow2006/4760658630/sizes/o/in/photostream/&#038;fl_ev=0&#038;lang=en&#038;intl=us\" alt=\"\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" /></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>然后，iWatermelon会根据反馈回来的声音进行判断，告诉你这个西瓜如何：</span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div>\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div><img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4080/4760027797_3213dc6d69_m.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://geo.yahoo.com/f?s=792600099&#038;t=db38784c2684b82ba22830d54b7e92ee&#038;r=http://www.flickr.com/photos/betashow2006/4760027797/sizes/o/in/photostream/&#038;fl_ev=0&#038;lang=en&#038;intl=us\" alt=\"\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" /></td>\n<td>\n<div><img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4117/4760666466_7376d302a5_m.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://geo.yahoo.com/f?s=792600099&#038;t=fd85e2fa5a78c449b17256dbe09ffa14&#038;r=http://www.flickr.com/photos/betashow2006/4760666466/sizes/o/in/photostream/&#038;fl_ev=0&#038;lang=en&#038;intl=us\" alt=\"\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" /></td>\n<td>\n<div><img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4117/4760025711_be3b702bed_m.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://geo.yahoo.com/f?s=792600099&#038;t=2eb62e7e4d81c20a7916f4c926956d40&#038;r=http://www.flickr.com/photos/betashow2006/4760025711/sizes/o/in/photostream/&#038;fl_ev=0&#038;lang=en&#038;intl=us\" alt=\"\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" /></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span>不同的声音反馈会得到三种不同的建议，如果三颗心都绿了，那说明这个西瓜那是“顶呱呱”，一定要买下哦。</span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span>这个定价0.99美金的应用非常简单，但却非常实用，通过建立一个简单的声音数据库来对不同颜色大小的西瓜成熟与否做出区别，然后通过iPhone麦克／动力传感器来搜集来自西瓜的反馈，并对比数据库做出判断，实在是妙，妙，妙！</span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span>iWatermelon在中国台湾，以色列和中国大陆这些喜欢吃西瓜的国度都一度达到“娱乐类应用”下载排名第一，希望对大家有所启发，开发出简单实用又赚钱的手机应用！</span></div>\n</p>\n<div><b><a href=\"http://blog.blogbus.com/?utm_source=blogbus&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=blog\">群博录：每个博客，都有故事……</a></b></div>\n<div>收藏到：<span><a href=\"http://delicious.com/save?url=http://betashow.blogbus.com/logs/73974170.html&#038;title=%E7%94%A8iPhone%E6%8C%91%E8%A5%BF%E7%93%9C%EF%BC%8C%E8%A1%8C%E5%90%97%EF%BC%9F\">Del.icio.us</a></span></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/t1/407464677/betashow_blogbus_com/blogbus.com/s.gif?r=http://betashow.blogbus.com/logs/73974170.html\" border=\"0\" height=\"0\" width=\"0\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/l/blogbus.com/betashow_blogbus_com/407464677/art01.html\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/i/blogbus.com/betashow_blogbus_com/407464677/art01.gif\"></a></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.tongji.linezing.com/1017243/tongji.gif\" /><img src=\"http://img.tongji.linezing.com/997968/tongji.gif\" /></p>\n<p>“要翻墙，<a href=\"http://idajiangyou.info\" target=\"_blank\">用赛风”</a>.</p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[8800]}